Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？要出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前說過吧 社團活動的合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊唔…貌似有說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時離家一陣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？孤零零地看家？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷清啦 我也要跟去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 祈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集說不要我來著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了啦 放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是大島來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:00:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去見見爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到啦到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好天氣呀 幸好天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說接下來去的地方是集親戚家的別墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小時候住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 大救星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂館颯太？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我班的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 帶他來大島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入那邊的GHQ設施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破防衛系統需要他的虛空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}突破防衛系統需要他的{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請他旅行而已 不是難事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要珍惜同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯那家伙 不懂人家的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害！氣派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿同學的親戚做什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這豪宅怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯說是供奉院集團安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倆人又要好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好回家要好去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷不防地說…說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆住一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倆人一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小打聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倆人是怎麽認識的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 我和祈之間什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有個粗暴的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我認識的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 藉口省了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋下幸福的贏家們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起就去大海啦 大海！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先整理…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事推後推後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來勝地 現在要玩個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂館同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好強硬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才像颯太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和颯太合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強硬 大老粗 不識相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是任務 一起來破旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破…旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 祭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也游啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來魂館颯太平安抵達了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身負任務卻骨頭輕飄飄地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他們玩沒關係麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止進行順利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是設施的防衛系統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶫正在調查那邊兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時待命麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這破島上有什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是非涯不知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來有吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不熱麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？集呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說有地方要去 先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來大島是集爸爸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 大小姐的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶫！那身可笑的打扮什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也十分般配綾瀨大小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿黑周博士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊天王洲大學的教授
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是研究天啟病毒的第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}也是研究{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Apocalypse Virus{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}的第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為家裡不談這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是春夏的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之記不得爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落聖誕麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Lost X'MAS{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天起一切都變了樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來怎麼來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是掃墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GHQ的秘密設施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有要找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源之石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們必須獲得的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回作戰計劃的關鍵在你和你抽出的虛空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}這回作戰計劃的關鍵在你和你抽出的{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂館颯太 懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始在2200
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前帶他來指定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實很簡單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用誘餌就成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘餌？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他是EGOIST的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用祈？我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不要？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用對方感興趣的東西 釣上鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基礎中的基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是祈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有繼續討論的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的話可以不做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡大覺去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有和朋友一起旅行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝花音肯一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是影研成員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是幽靈成員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是谷尋同學沒來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和他沒關係吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大救星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和楪兩個人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祈皮膚好美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 可以摸不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 光滑光滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那邊不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楪對集什麼想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和祈之間真的什麼都沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不也說了 真的什麼都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒的話我要上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈…我要上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連累朋友的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿不適合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意見不同吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有連累才有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒冒險的人生多無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人內心裡多少得掀起些波瀾吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恙神…涯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是我的孩子還沒個定說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的母親不是個好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不同吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 冷不防地…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星好美呢 在東京難得…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是東京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他們獨處也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西想給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了EGOIST的PV超感動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐立不安地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自己也做了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥名堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}?盛開呀 田野花兒喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}?啊啊 求求你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}?人們為什麼 互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}?互相爭吵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抄我的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為人人都能靠它引起祈的注意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈…祈！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不怎麼瞭解祈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊！對唱著歌的你超級感動 真心的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想更多地瞭解祈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真心…喜…喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 幹啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在這裡抽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 幾時起蹲那兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好沒耐心的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈是我的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料外的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 涯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃不變 照常進行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噯噯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈是我的…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員到齊了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶫已經搞定警衛的視野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是內部 大雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白要說完整
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那相機拍門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是「開啟」虛空？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}難道這是「開啟」{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬下得罪 莖道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過路亡靈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道露餡兒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是我們 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼颯太身體裡會出來這種虛空？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}為什麼颯太身體裡會出來這種{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言什麼理由無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個虛空還能開啟這種機關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}那個{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}還能開啟這種機關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標物在前方 拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯 幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你麼 莖道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的痛苦 莫過於念叨幸福時光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑周
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？祈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要幫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然對祈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想的話開頭就說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得你腦子裡想的什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯太也是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天那麼強硬 大老粗 不識相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭你這種地方啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和颯太合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招他厭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友就不得不說出真心話來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你坦白說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集啊 總有距離感不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我過去也和你合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以幸好你說出真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算對我敞開心門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止一知半解的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這樣不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這右手 觸碰到的是人心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空會根據心靈的形狀而改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}會根據心靈的形狀而改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那使心靈相通的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量也會變化麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}so everything that makes me whole
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:14.82,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}今君に捧げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:19.75,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}I'm yours
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:36.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}ねえ　この世界にはたくさんの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:42.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}幸せがあるんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:50.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}いつか二人なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:57.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}誰かが君のことを嘘つきと呼んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:02:02.74,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}心無い言葉で傷つけようとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:08.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}世界が君のことを信じようともせずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:14.32,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}茨の冠を被せようとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:20.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}私は君だけの味方になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:25.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}その孤独　痛みを私は知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:28.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}so everything that makes me whole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:35.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}今君に捧げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:25.92,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}もうあたなから愛されることも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:32.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}必要とされることもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:41.18,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}そして私はこうして一人ぼっちで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:49.29,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あの時あなたはなんって言ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:55.90,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}届かない言葉は宙を舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:22:02.66,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}わかってるのに今日もしてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:09.28,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}叶わぬ願いごとを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:19.46,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}離さないで　ぎゅっと手を握ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:26.32,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あなたと二人続くと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:35.15,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}繋いだその手は暖かくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:43.13,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}優しかった
